Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,选手休息室2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz117\pos(1030,430)}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz113\pos(1158,426)}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.2\pos(1828,664)}选手休息室2
